channel.title: God Wars Dungeon
channel.description:
The GWD is being added quite soon and im here to give you some information about the dungeon.
A Video made by one of my friends [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qE2Pue7U82Y[/youtube]
First off the dungeon. There will be many monsters in there and they will be from all factions Bandos,Saradomin,Zamorak,and Armadyl. To Enter the Bandos area you need 70 Strength and don't forgot your hammer or you can't get in the room! To Enter the Armadyl area you need 70 Range and don't forget your Grappling Hook! To Enter the Zamorak Aren you need 70 Hitpoints. To Enter the Saradomin Area you need 70 Agility.
There are many items that make a type of factions monsters not fight you right when you enter.
Bandos -Bandos Runeplated Armour -Blessed Bandos d'hide Armour -Ancient Mace -Bandos Robes -Bandos Cloak -Bandos Stole Armadyl -Blessed Armadyl D'hide Armour -Armadyl Pendant -Armadyl Robes -Armadyl Cloak -Armadyl Stole Saradomin -Saradomin Rune Plated Armour -Saradomin Stole -Saradomin Cloak -Blessed Saradomin D'hide Armour -Holy Book Zamorak -Zamorak Rune Plated Armour -Blessed Zamorak D'hide Armour -Zamorak Stole -Zamorak Cloak -Unholy Book
[b]MORE INFORMATION COMING SOON![/b]
